# Header

## Container
- Layout: flex row with responsive stacking
- Padding: `px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8 py-3`

## Search Bar
- BG: `bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Border radius: `rounded-[100px]` (pill)
- Padding: `p-3 md:p-4`
- Max width: `md:max-w-[560px] lg:w-[560px]`
- Icon: `Search size-6`
- Input: transparent bg, placeholder styling
- This is a standalone search — does NOT use `TextField`

## Action Links
- "What's New" and "Contact Us" — hidden on mobile
- Standard hyperlink styling

## Profile Avatar
- BG: `bg-[#f5f9fe]`
- Border: `border border-[#e0e0e0]`
- Size: `size-9 md:size-10`
- Shape: `rounded-full`
- Content: bold initials centered
